# Pandora's Box - Self-Hosted AI Stack

## Tech Stack
- **Framework**: Next.js 14 (App Router)
- **Backend**: Firebase (Firestore, Auth, Admin SDK)
- **Vector Database**: Qdrant
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS
- **Deployment**: Google Cloud Run

## Design System
- **Style**: Apple-esque glassmorphism
- **Theme**: "Digital Void" Cyberpunk Glassmorphism
- **Components**: shadcn/ui primitives with custom glassmorphism utilities

## Architecture Principles
- **Sovereign**: All AI processing uses local vLLM (no external APIs)
- **Self-Hosted**: Qdrant for vector storage, local inference endpoints
- **Server-Side**: Processing happens on server (API Routes/Lib)
- **Asynchronous**: Background processing for heavy operations

## Code Standards
- TypeScript strict mode
- Server Actions for data mutations
- Firebase Admin SDK for server-side operations
- CORS handling for all API routes
